A vintage 1960s illustration style image depicting a ornate wooden rolodex sitting on a mahogany desk, with some contact cards visibly tucked deeper inside behind frosted glass dividers while others remain accessible at the front. A brass skeleton key rests beside the rolodex, and soft afternoon light streams through venetian blinds casting striped shadows across the scene. The color palette features warm amber, deep brown, and cream tones with subtle paper texture throughout the composition.
